name: You've-woke-up-late-and-you-have-a-9am-and-don't-want-to-dissapoint-carlo simulator
description:
OH NO! You've woke up late, grab the essentials and run for the bus in time at 9! if you miss the bus that's it you are off the course, Carlo is still mad at you for uploading 2 weeks after the deadline of the last project. 

Objects are randomly generated all across the house and garden, find then all for the win

Move with WASD

Click to pick up

Release to yeet

Click the glowing yellow items to pick up, (the food isnt glowing dont worry, its safe)

 Each day completed will increase your score get the highscore!
